# domains list

there are a bunch of random websites covering the sog wide web
this page covers them all in excruciating detail! enjoy!

## websites owned by ssoggycat

:sog: [_soggy.cat_](https://soggy.cat/) - the (un)official soggy cat website, for all things sog
-# [_s.soggy.cat_](https://s.soggy.cat/) - hey, you're here right now!
-# [_drive, drive2, & drive3.soggy.cat_](https://drive3.soggy.cat/) - shortcuts to the soggy drives, drive3 being the most popular (add /github to drive3 for the github version)
-# [_this.soggy.cat_](https://this.soggy.cat/) - for a ssoggycat bit
-# [_hourly.soggy.cat_](https://hourly.soggy.cat/) - supe4cookie's "soggy cat every hour" discord bot
<br>
:sog: [_soggy.world_](https://soggy.world/) - brought back from the dead, redirects to our discord server!
-# [_googlandia.soggy.world_](https://googlandia.soggy.world/) - goog...landia's discord
-# [_canny.soggy.world_](https://canny.soggy.world/) - canny world's discord
<br>
:sog: [sgggy.cat](https://sgggy.cat/) - for a substitute function trick on discord
-# send [https://soggy.cat/](https://soggy.cat/), then send **s/o/g** and an image of shark will jump out of the embed!
<br>
:sog: [_sogfulday.today_](https://sogfulday.today/) - mat's tinkering domain (with a great frontpage and error page)
-# [_cdn.sogfulday.today_](https://cdn.sogfulday.today/gifs/dancing.gif) - important screenshots, random gifs and other files for preservation
-# [_drive, drive2, & drive3.sogfulday.today_](https://drive3.sogfulday.today/) - older shortcuts to the soggy drives. only kept around to not break old links
<br>
:sog: [_🐱💧.to_](https://xn--5o8hmh.to/) - currently redirects to the <span class="small">dead</span> bluesky account
<br>
:sog: [_hydrowa.re_](https://hydrowa.re/) - de-facto branch of ssoggycat for games & more related to development (on hiatus)
<br>
:sog: [_guweh.com_](https://guweh.com/) - literally guweh
-# [mirror.guweh.com](https://mirror.guweh.com/images.json) - a dynamically updated mirror of drive3.
-# you can get paths to all [images](https://mirror.guweh.com/images.json), [videos](https://mirror.guweh.com/videos.json), and additionally [all images in WebP format](https://mirror.guweh.com/webp.json)
